Gatara::

"Negatory," Gatara dismisses the notion with a wave of her hand.  
"They'll be back soon.  I expect Jayde will need some time in the CR 
- she never learns."

The brownish-green bot places a hand on Noir's shoulder.  "Don't let 
it get to you.  Everyone messes up once in a while, and we've had 
setbacks before.  We'll recover, just like we always do."

> -- Noir --
> 
> Noir stares at the sensory display of the Rogue Star, the glances 
at 
> Gatara and the console. The Rogues' initial mission had been a 
> failure... The black assassin/tech didn't like failure, regardless 
> of the fact that there were circumstances beyond her control.
> 
> "Failure..." She frowns, "Should I go and meet Devilcat and the 
> others?" Her words were now mostly directed to herself, but she 
also 
> expected Gatara to have an opinion. 
> 
> "Has Devilcat given you a status report?" She keeps talking,
